name: Donglu Bunny Girl Style
description:
Textual Inversion of the Art-Style and especially the Bunny Girl from Donglu Yu

I love the style and tried to bake it in a TI, which is hard cuz the TI can only use whats in a model. So this might work good on some models and not so good on others.

The bunny girl is pretty strong embedded, and every character gets bunny ears.

Have fun playing around with this.

More Cyberpunk-Style from Donglu will be added here too i guess, we will see how that works out.
